# ==========================================
# MARKETPLEACE - Environment Configuration
# ==========================================
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# cp .env.example .env.local

# ==========================================
# 1. FIREBASE CLIENT CONFIGURATION
# (Untuk frontend - browser/client side)
# ==========================================
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_project_id.firebaseapp.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your_project_id.appspot.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your_sender_id
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your_app_id
NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# ==========================================
# 2. FIREBASE ADMIN CONFIGURATION
# (Untuk backend/server-side operations)
# 
# PILIH SALAH SATU METODE DI BAWAH:
# ==========================================

# --- METODE 1: GCP Service Account JSON (RECOMMENDED) ---
# Dapatkan dari Firebase Console > Project Settings > Service Accounts > Generate new private key
# Paste seluruh isi file JSON di sini (dalam satu baris atau multi-line)
GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY='{"type":"service_account","project_id":"your_project_id","private_key_id":"...","private_key":"-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n","client_email":"firebase-adminsdk-xxxxx@your_project_id.iam.gserviceaccount.com","client_id":"...","auth_uri":"https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/auth","token_uri":"https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token","auth_provider_x509_cert_url":"https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v1/certs","client_x509_cert_url":"https://www.googleapis.com/robot/v1/metadata/x509/firebase-adminsdk-xxxxx%40your_project_id.iam.gserviceaccount.com"}'

# --- METODE 2: Individual Environment Variables (ALTERNATIF) ---
# Gunakan ini jika tidak ingin menggunakan JSON utuh
# FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
# FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=firebase-adminsdk-xxxxx@your_project_id.iam.gserviceaccount.com
# FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nYour_Private_Key_Here\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"

# ==========================================
# 3. EMAIL CONFIGURATION (Nodemailer)
# ==========================================
# Untuk Gmail, gunakan App Password (bukan password biasa)
# Aktifkan 2-Step Verification dulu, lalu generate App Password di:
# https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
EMAIL_PORT=587
EMAIL_USER=your_email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your_gmail_app_password
EMAIL_FROM="ATAYATOKO <noreply@atayatoko.aty0.com>"

# ==========================================
# 4. SMS CONFIGURATION (Twilio)
# ==========================================
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_twilio_account_sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_twilio_auth_token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890

# ==========================================
# 5. BRI PAYMENT GATEWAY
# ==========================================
BRI_CLIENT_ID=your_bri_client_id
BRI_CLIENT_SECRET=your_bri_client_secret
BRI_API_URL=https://api.bri.co.id

# ==========================================
# 6. APPLICATION SETTINGS
# ==========================================
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://atayatoko.aty0.com
NODE_ENV=production

# ==========================================
# 7. OPTIONAL: PWA & ANALYTICS
# ==========================================
DISABLE_PWA=false
ANALYZE=false

# ==========================================
# CARA MENDAPATKAN FIREBASE ADMIN CREDENTIALS
# ==========================================

## METODE 1: Menggunakan GCP Service Account JSON (RECOMMENDED)

### Langkah-langkah:

1. **Buka Firebase Console**
   - Kunjungi https://console.firebase.google.com/
   - Pilih project Anda

2. **Navigasi ke Service Accounts**
   - Klik icon gear (⚙️) di sebelah "Project Overview"
   - Pilih "Project settings"
   - Pindah ke tab "Service accounts"

3. **Generate Private Key**
   - Di bagian "Firebase Admin SDK", klik "Generate new private key"
   - Konfirmasi dengan klik "Generate key"
   - File JSON akan otomatis terdownload (contoh: `your-project-firebase-adminsdk-xxxxx.json`)

4. **Copy Isi File JSON**
   - Buka file JSON yang baru didownload
   - Copy SELURUH konten JSON
   - Paste ke variabel `GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY` di `.env.local`
   
   Contoh format:
   ```
   GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY='{"type":"service_account","project_id":"your-project-id",...}'
   ```

5. **Verifikasi**
   - Jalankan `npm run build`
   - Pastikan tidak ada warning "Firebase Admin credentials not fully provided"

---

## METODE 2: Menggunakan Individual Environment Variables

Jika Anda lebih suka menggunakan variabel terpisah, extract nilai-nilai berikut dari file JSON service account:

1. **FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID**
   - Ambil dari field `"project_id"` di JSON
   
2. **FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL**
   - Ambil dari field `"client_email"` di JSON
   - Format: `firebase-adminsdk-xxxxx@your-project-id.iam.gserviceaccount.com`

3. **FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY**
   - Ambil dari field `"private_key"` di JSON
   - PENTING: Pastikan format newline benar (`\n`)
   - Jangan hapus header/footer: `-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----` dan `-----END PRIVATE KEY-----`

Contoh:
```bash
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=firebase-adminsdk-xxxxx@your-project-id.iam.gserviceaccount.com
FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nMIIEvQIBADANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQEFAASCBKcwggSjAgEAAoIBAQC...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
```

---

## DEPLOYMENT KE VERCEL

Untuk production deployment di Vercel:

1. **Via Dashboard Vercel:**
   - Buka project Anda di Vercel
   - Settings → Environment Variables
   - Tambahkan semua variabel dari `.env.example`
   - Untuk `GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY`, paste seluruh JSON dalam satu baris

2. **Via Vercel CLI:**
   ```bash
   vercel env add GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY
   # Paste JSON value ketika diminta
   ```

3. **Redeploy:**
   ```bash
   vercel --prod
   ```

---

## TROUBLESHOOTING

### Warning: "Firebase Admin credentials not fully provided"

**Penyebab:** Tidak ada metode credentials yang dikonfigurasi dengan benar

**Solusi:**
1. Pastikan Anda mengisi SALAH SATU metode (JSON atau individual)
2. Untuk JSON: pastikan format valid (gunakan JSON validator online)
3. Untuk individual: pastikan ketiga variabel (PROJECT_ID, CLIENT_EMAIL, PRIVATE_KEY) terisi

### Error: "Error parsing GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY"

**Penyebab:** Format JSON tidak valid atau ada karakter escape yang salah

**Solusi:**
1. Validasi JSON di https://jsonlint.com/
2. Pastikan quotes dan special characters di-escape dengan benar
3. Coba gunakan Metode 2 (individual variables) sebagai alternatif

### Error saat deploy ke Vercel

**Penyebab:** Environment variables belum diset di Vercel

**Solusi:**
1. Set semua environment variables di Vercel dashboard
2. Redeploy setelah menambahkan variables
3. Cek logs di Vercel untuk error details

---

## KEAMANAN

⚠️ **PENTING:**
- JANGAN pernah commit file `.env.local` ke Git
- JANGAN share service account JSON di public repository
- Gunakan App Password untuk Gmail (bukan password utama)
- Rotate credentials secara berkala
- Jika credentials bocor, segera revoke di Firebase Console dan generate yang baru

